type="submit">&lt;&lt;&gt;<[MALICIOUS PAYLOAD EXECUTION!]> "></p>
<p class="autoupdate_bar" style="display:none;">&nbsp; Update in progress...<br><img src="admin/themes/default/images/ajax-loader-bar.gif"></p>
